                            dst-mac ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff
                            etype 0x8848
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 666 create
                        action accept
                        description "0x8848/MPLS multicast/Multicast"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            dst-mac 01:00:5e:00:00:00 ff:ff:ff:80:00:00
                            etype 0x8848
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 699 create
                        action accept
                        description "0x8848/MPLS multicast/Others"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            etype 0x8848
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 733 create
                        action accept
                        description "0x8863/PPPoE Discovery/PADI/Broadcast"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            dst-mac ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff
                            etype 0x8863
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 766 create
                        action accept
                        description "0x8863/PPPoE Discovery/----/Multicast"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            dst-mac 01:00:5e:00:00:00 ff:ff:ff:80:00:00
                            etype 0x8863
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 799 create
                        action accept
                        description "0x8863/PPPoE Discovery/PADR/Others"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            etype 0x8863
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 833 create
                        action accept
                        description "0x8864/PPPoE Session/Broadcast"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            dst-mac ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff

                        exit
                    exit

                        exit
                    exit

                    dot1p-out-profile 4

                    dscp-out-profile cs1

                    lsp-exp-out-profile 1
                    dot1p-in-profile 1
                    dot1p-out-profile 1
                exit
                fc nc
                    dscp-in-profile nc1
                    dscp-out-profile nc1
                    lsp-exp-in-profile 6
                    lsp-exp-out-profile 6
                    dot1p-in-profile 6
                    dot1p-out-profile 6
                exit
            exit
        exit

            description "for marking"

                dscp cs1 fc l2 profile in
